---
# var-naming[no-role-prefix]: public role vars follow technology-convention naming
# (mssql_*, grafana_*, perfmon_*) and private task vars use _* ephemeral convention,
# enforcing the role-prefix on both would require renaming well-established inventory
# variable names without any real benefit especially for roles that won't be part of
# ansible galaxy

skip_list:
  - var-naming[no-role-prefix]
